THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS
================================================================================

This script uses the following Nmap NSE libraries, which are part of Nmap:
- http.lua - HTTP library (Nmap license)
- json.lua - JSON parsing (Nmap license)
- shortport.lua - Port rule library (Nmap license)
- stdnse.lua - Standard NSE library (Nmap license)

These libraries remain under their respective Nmap licenses.

